---
description: Supabase access patterns in SvelteKit
globs: src/lib/server/**,src/hooks.server.ts,src/routes/**
alwaysApply: false
---

# Data access rules

- Per-request Supabase client via @supabase/ssr in hooks.server.ts,
  exposed on event.locals (locals.supabase, locals.safeGetSession)
- Reads in +page.server.ts load functions; writes in form actions.
  No client-side writes to database tables.
- Service-role key only in src/lib/server, only for platform-operator
  functions. Never import server modules into client code.
- Env via $env/static/private and $env/static/public — never process.env
- Validate all form action inputs (zod) before touching the database
